<exercise number="1"><statement><p>Apply the first law of exponents to find the product.<ol label="a" cols="3">
    <li><m>x^3 \cdot x^6</m></li>
    <li><m>5^6 \cdot 5^8</m></li>
    <li><m>b^3(b)(b^5)</m></li></ol></p></statement>
<answer><p><ol label="a" cols="3">
    <li><p><m>x^9</m></p></li>
    <li><p><m>5^{14}</m></p></li>
    <li><p><m>b^9</m></p></li></ol></p></answer></exercise>

